label: Tyumen region today
title: Tyumenskaya_oblastʹ_segodnya
exrest: Tyumenskaya oblastʹ segodnya is a daily Russian socio-political tabloid. The area of distribution covers the territory of Tyumen region, Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug, Yamalo-Nenets Autonomous Okrug. The newspaper is an official newspaper of the Government of the Tyumen Region. The newspaper publishes the official decrees, statements and documents of regional bodies. This includes the promulgation of newly approved laws. Regional government documents and legislative instruments come into force after their publication in the newspaper.
